            <head altrender="biography" id="a2">BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE </head>
            <p>Professor of Education in the College of Agriculture and Life Sciences at Cornell University.  Millman was an expert on standardized testing methods.  He was also active in the Suicide Prevention and Crisis Service in Tompkins County, N.Y.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
            <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
